title: Junglers Are Getting Dumber Every Season
body: Don't ever pick a Supportive ADC in any ELO below Plat. Even with Ashe Ulti, Ezreal Iceborn, or Varus Ulti, no one will ever gank for you. They only gank the lane who whines the most in solo q. Doesn't matter if enemy bot has been shoving for 10mins, by the 20min mark, they can't be counted on.
